---

import "react-image-gallery/styles/css/image-gallery.css";

import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Slideshow from "../components/Slides";
---

<style>
.image-gallery-thumbnails-container {
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: max-content;
  }
</style>

<Layout title="All About Paws">
  <h2>All About Paws Pet Spa, LLC.</h2>
  <Slideshow 
    client:only={'preact'}
  />
  <div
    class="flex flex-col-reverse space-x-9 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-center md:space-x-0 md:space-y-4"
  >
    <p class="w-full md:mr-4">
      {` `}
       All About Paws Pet Spa LLC. is a locally owned business providing
      full-service grooming for dogs and cats. My core belief is that every
      animal is unique and requires customized treatment. While many pets come
      in with tails wagging in happy anticipation of being groomed, others are
      more anxious. For this reason, I always spend a few minutes "meeting" your
      pet and helping them get to know me before I start grooming.
      <br />
      <br />
       Kindness, understanding, knowledge, and experience are the keys to great
      grooming, so I go out of my way to treat every animal with gentleness and
      respect - the way I treat my own pets. As I have 20 plus years in the
      professional grooming industry, you can rest assured your beloved pet will
      be in good hands.
      <br />
      <br />
       Call to hear more about All About Paws, or just come on over to say,
      "Hello!"
    </p>

    <aside
      class="border-gray-200 mb-2 flex w-full
                flex-row items-start justify-between space-y-0
                border-b-2 md:mb-0 md:h-full md:w-auto md:flex-col md:space-y-6 md:border-b-0 md:border-l-2"
      style={{ marginLeft: "0 !important" }}
    >
      <a
        target="_blank"
        referrerpolicy={"no-referrer"}
        class="text-accent nav_link w-fit content-center items-center text-md md:w-full md:text-lg"
        href={import.meta.env.GOOGLE_REVIEWS_URL}
      >
        Reviews
      </a>
      <a
        target="_blank"
        referrerpolicy={"no-referrer"}
        class="text-accent nav_link w-fit content-center items-center text-center text-md md:w-full md:text-left md:text-lg"
        href={import.meta.env.GOOGLE_WRITE_REVIEW}
      >
        Write a Review
      </a>

      <div
        class="hidden h-px w-full border-b-2 border-dashed border-b-gray-dark md:block"
      >
        <br />
      </div>

      <iframe
        class="hidden md:block"
        sandbox="allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-same-origin allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-downloads allow-modals"
        aria-label="Map, 16329 Co Rd V"
        src="https://maps-api-ssl.google.com/maps?hl=en&ll=40.305269,-103.844805&output=embed&q=16329+Co+Rd+V,+Fort+Morgan,+CO+80701,+USA+(16329+Co+Rd+V)&z=16"
        allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
      <a
        class="text-green-600 nav_link w-fit content-center items-center text-center text-md md:w-full md:text-left md:text-lg"
        href={import.meta.env.GOOGLE_DIRECTION_URL}
        target="_blank"
        referrerpolicy={"no-referrer"}
      >
        Get Directions
      </a>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>benefits of regular bathing &#38; Grooming</h2>
    <div
      class="equal-columns mt-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 lg:flex-row"
    >
      <img
        class="w-full md:w-1/4 md:mb-0 md:mr-4"
        src="/assets/images/sitting_dog.png"
        loading="lazy"
        alt=""
      />

      <ul role="list" class="w-full md:w-2/4 space-y-4 text-center">
        <li>Healthy skin and coat. Less shedding!</li>
        <li>
          Less stress of having to lift and struggle to get your pet into the
          bathtub.
        </li>
        <li>Trimmed nails are safer for your pet and you. Also the floor!</li>
        <li>Decreased amount of matting.</li>
        <li>Your pet will look and smell great.</li>
        <li>
          Potential health risks may be spotted before they become major
          complications.
        </li>
        <li>
          Pet becomes accustomed to being bathed. This leads to more enjoyment
          from the experience!
        </li>
      </ul>

      <img
        class="w-full md:w-1/4 md:mb-0 md:mr-4"
        src="/assets/images/sitting_cat.png"
        loading="lazy"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Move above content to a table format */}
</Layout>
